    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Structures supported by a series of double cables of different curvature used in the same vertical plane and held apart by struts in compression.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
